<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/103000387/2025-26/evaluation> a ns1:EvaluationSystem ;
    ns1:evaluationDescription """Progressive assessment consists of a presentation (30%) and an exam (70%). Both components are recoverable. However, the exam is not recoverable during the global evaluation, as it takes place during the official exam week.

In the global evaluation, the presentation may be recovered by taking an exam that accounts for 100% of the final grade.

During the extraordinary evaluation period, a single exam will also be administered, which will account for 100% of the final grade."""@es ;
